channel.title: Comments on: I’d Rather be in Norrath

item.title: By: DensityDuck
item.dc:creator: DensityDuck
item.description:
Saw a guy driving out of Yahoo! the other day, with the license plate "SOW PLZ"
I can only guess at how much he paid to get that one.

item.title: By: Foton
item.dc:creator: Foton
item.description:
Guess it wouldn't be fair for me to guess since I can check your IP.
Saw someone in my state with "WTF(+ four random digits)". I was immediately envious.
